name: Vhodekar Restaurant & Bar

reviews.review_text:
I recently had the pleasure of dining here and I was thoroughly impressed. From the moment I stepped through the door, I was greeted with warm hospitality and a inviting atmosphere. The restaurant's decor is elegant yet comfortable, creating a relaxing and enjoyable dining experience.

The menu boasts a wide variety of dishes, showcasing a creative blend of flavors and fresh ingredients. , Food quality was good.

The service was impeccable, The staff's friendly demeanor added to the overall positive experience.

Just need improve goan dish  taste

Vhodekar in Mapusa is well-known for its fish thali and a variety of other dishes. Personally, I really enjoy the fish thali here and have visited multiple times. However, occasionally the fish isn't as fresh as I'd like. One of my favorite items from the thali is the pineapple sausav, which is delicious. Their chicken dishes are also worth trying – well-dressed and flavorful. The staff is friendly, and the vibe is quite nice. Be prepared for a wait during the afternoons, especially on weekends. On the downside, the washroom could be cleaner, and parking is a bit tricky. Overall, it's a satisfying experience.

Great place for fish/prawns thali at unbelievably low prices. The food is excellent. 1 star less as the prawn thali had only 3 large prawns. Suggestion to charge more and increase the quantity of prawns in the thali.

description:
### Vhodekar Restaurant & Bar: A Taste of Goa in Tivim

Nestled in the vibrant heart of Tivim, Vhodekar Restaurant & Bar boasts a commendable rating of 3.8, reflecting the sentiments of nearly 900 diners. This well-frequented establishment is particularly celebrated for its **Goan cuisine** (36 mentions), with must-try offerings like the **fish thali** (23 mentions) and a delightful selection of **seafood** (19 mentions), including the notable **barramundi** (14 mentions). The combination of its inviting atmosphere and acclaimed dishes positions Vhodekar as a beloved destination for both locals and visitors seeking authentic Goan flavors.

### Ambiance & Design

Upon entering Vhodekar, guests are greeted with warm hospitality that sets the tone for a memorable dining experience. The restaurant features an elegant yet comfortable decor characterized by rustic wooden accents, soft lighting, and artistic touches that reflect Goan culture. Diners appreciate the intimate atmosphere, ideal for both casual meals and special gatherings. The relaxed vibe is further enhanced by a thoughtfully curated playlist that complements the setting, creating an overall enjoyable ambiance.

![Vhodekar Interior](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdms0xWnQ_WRNK1Dx57tDdVnvi9jQGDK3DM8HuJk1co5HxCOGtPt5UoutJRo2aQ7KMgFlwZAmhktA_qCKk_xxDneS35gWVSOS7zcPS6oYjlzH-0rfJ7WdQdAGGikzj7LT6cUZEW9=w375-h281-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

Food at Vhodekar is where the magic truly happens. The menu is a testament to Goa’s rich culinary heritage, showcasing a variety of dishes that consistently highlight fresh local ingredients and vibrant flavors. The **fish thali**, a fan favorite, is often lauded for its delightful combinations, with reviewers particularly enjoying the pineapple sausav that accompanies it. Diners also appreciate the comparative affordability of the seafood offerings, making it a great value for the quality.

While the overall presentation of the dishes exudes care and artistry, some patrons have expressed a desire for improvements in certain Goan specialties. Reviewers have noted that occasionally the fish has not been as fresh, which could impact the overall dining experience. However, the quality and flavor of dishes like the chicken preparations have received high praise. Additionally, Vhodekar’s menu offers ample options for those with varying dietary preferences, emphasizing inclusivity and customer satisfaction.

![Delicious Seafood](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdm__v5rykwn-sX4r_YATIw-spt7QhLlouIgrXNlNvpelrKVJN-yuSf6T098Oc0YZ4ywYYt2cynLBNH1dEjqKYD2y2uKHCAulz8zN9DFGr8UE_3diOEZXK6RX2HD-3Ijl2nx9HCI=w375-h281-p)

### Customer Experience & Service

The customer experience at Vhodekar is generally characterized by friendly and efficient service. Many patrons have commended the staff for their attentiveness and welcoming demeanor, contributing positively to the overall dining atmosphere. However, some diners have highlighted the importance of being prepared for longer wait times, especially during peak hours on weekends. While reservations are recommended, walk-ins are also welcome, but a little patience may be required on bustling days.

On the cleanliness front, there have been mentions of the need for improved maintenance in the washroom facilities, an area that could use some attention to match the otherwise inviting conditions of the restaurant.

### Popularity & Reviews

Vhodekar has gained a loyal following, with numerous repeat customers returning primarily for its celebrated fish thali and seafood dishes. Social media buzz often echoes similar sentiments, as patrons share their delicious experiences and recommend the restaurant to friends and family. Although the restaurant maintains a generally favorable outlook, the concerns shared by customers regarding freshness and cleanliness serve as constructive feedback that, if addressed, could elevate the dining experience further.

![Seafood Presentation](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmv13_jP6VkOxKnLf_QL27FABzKBE4YvwhB7g8NnTq1hLW0hKXilA_zyQeaHjmG_DRz-5p2ySx9reUe9HoFKVtcO3fcKLAa8bb401wnK_OuIQuNd3yZZXaDqRHdeCsyZD42yGdV5Q=w375-h281-p)

### Conclusion

In summary, Vhodekar Restaurant & Bar stands out as a convivial dining spot in Tivim, inviting diners to indulge in a culinary journey through Goa. With its flavorful **fish thali**, welcoming atmosphere, and committed service, it remains a must-visit spot for seafood lovers and those keen on experiencing genuine Goan hospitality. As the restaurant continues to refine its offerings, it promises to enhance the dining experience even further for both newcomers and devoted fans alike.
